summary: This mod adds a Set of eyes for the player character...(all vanilla races and genders included)
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3750/10139912214_65b1b27d82.jpg[/img]
[img]http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3767/9983429746_b7a2023905.jpg[/img]

[youtube]s6UkXxKeU2g[/youtube] [youtube]vxt_BwzNTys[/youtube]
video by gruntlock                      video by Muzzammil12

This mod adds a Set of eyes for the player character...
I am not going for realism ...so dont ask :D.
for Ninghiem compatibility use [URL=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/44445/?tab=2&navtag=%2Fajax%2Fmodfiles%2F%3Fid%3D44445&pUp=1]Runic Eyes for Ningheim Compatibility Patch[/URL]
[img]http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3710/9952354835_8b415b9132.jpg[/img]
